TopicTitle: Is MKS compatible with planet packs?

Articles.Content:
I kinda want to play RSS Constellations and colonize absolutely anything that could be colonized, using MKS.

But I was wondering if RSS planets will have the resources of MKS on them ( such as gypsum or hydrates )

If they don't, then my whole playthrough will be useless. Help?
You should really be asking on the MKS and RSS mod threads...that's where the modders and players for those mods hang out.
If the folders for the planet packs have any files or whatever marked CRP or CommunityResourcePack, they're probably compatible.
